b'[Sacred Texts](../../index.htm)  [Hinduism](../index.htm)  [Index](index.htm)  \n[English](../gita/bg08.htm)  \n[Previous](bgs07.htm)  [Next](bgs09.htm)\n\n* * *\n\nVIII. atha a\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadamodhy\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb8\xa5. (ak\xe1\xb9\xa3arabrahmayoga\xe1\xb8\xa5)  \n  \narjuna uv\xc4\x81ca  \n  \nki\xe1\xb9\x83 tad brahma kim adhy\xc4\x81tma\xe1\xb9\x83 ki\xe1\xb9\x83 karma  \npuru\xe1\xb9\xa3ottama  \nadhibh\xc5\xabta\xe1\xb9\x83 ca ki\xe1\xb9\x83 proktam adhidaiva\xe1\xb9\x83 kim ucyate  \n8.1  \n  \nadhiyaj\xc3\xb1a\xe1\xb8\xa5 katha\xe1\xb9\x83 kotra dehesmin madhus\xc5\xabdana  \npray\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87ak\xc4\x81le ca katha\xe1\xb9\x83 j\xc3\xb1eyosi niyat\xc4\x81tmabhi\xe1\xb8\xa5 8.2  \n  \n\xc5\x9br\xc4\xabbhagav\xc4\x81n uv\xc4\x81ca  \n  \nak\xe1\xb9\xa3ara\xe1\xb9\x83 brahma parama\xe1\xb9\x83 svabh\xc4\x81vodhy\xc4\x81tmam ucyate  \nbh\xc5\xabtabh\xc4\x81vodbhavakaro visarga\xe1\xb8\xa5 karmasa\xe1\xb9\x83j\xc3\xb1ita\xe1\xb8\xa5 8.3  \n  \nadhibh\xc5\xabta\xe1\xb9\x83 k\xe1\xb9\xa3aro bh\xc4\x81va\xe1\xb8\xa5 puru\xe1\xb9\xa3a\xc5\x9b c\xc4\x81dhidaivatam  \nadhiyaj\xc3\xb1oham ev\xc4\x81tra dehe dehabh\xe1\xb9\x9bt\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 vara 8.4  \n  \nantak\xc4\x81le ca m\xc4\x81m eva smaran muktv\xc4\x81 kalevaram  \nya\xe1\xb8\xa5 pray\xc4\x81ti sa madbh\xc4\x81va\xe1\xb9\x83 y\xc4\x81ti n\xc4\x81sty atra sa\xe1\xb9\x83\xc5\x9baya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n8.5  \n  \nya\xe1\xb9\x83 ya\xe1\xb9\x83 v\xc4\x81pi smaran bh\xc4\x81va\xe1\xb9\x83 tyajaty ante kalevaram  \nta\xe1\xb9\x83 tam evaiti kaunteya sad\xc4\x81 tadbh\xc4\x81vabh\xc4\x81vita\xe1\xb8\xa5 8.6  \n  \ntasm\xc4\x81t sarve\xe1\xb9\xa3u k\xc4\x81le\xe1\xb9\xa3u m\xc4\x81m anusmara yudhya ca  \nmayy arpitamanobuddhir m\xc4\x81m evai\xe1\xb9\xa3yasy asa\xe1\xb9\x83\xc5\x9baya\xe1\xb8\xa5 8.7  \n  \nabhy\xc4\x81sayogayuktena cetas\xc4\x81 n\xc4\x81nyag\xc4\x81min\xc4\x81  \nparama\xe1\xb9\x83 puru\xe1\xb9\xa3a\xe1\xb9\x83 divya\xe1\xb9\x83 y\xc4\x81ti p\xc4\x81rth\xc4\x81nucintayan 8.8  \n  \nkavi\xe1\xb9\x83 pur\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87am anu\xc5\x9b\xc4\x81sit\xc4\x81ra\xe1\xb9\x83  \na\xe1\xb9\x87or a\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\xaby\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83sam anusmared ya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nsarvasya dh\xc4\x81t\xc4\x81ram acintyar\xc5\xabpa\xe1\xb9\x83  \n\xc4\x81dityavar\xe1\xb9\x87a\xe1\xb9\x83 tamasa\xe1\xb8\xa5 parast\xc4\x81t 8.9  \n  \npray\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87ak\xc4\x81le manas\xc4\x81calena  \nbhakty\xc4\x81 yukto yogabalena caiva  \nbhruvor madhye pr\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87am \xc4\x81ve\xc5\x9bya samyak  \nsa ta\xe1\xb9\x83 para\xe1\xb9\x83 puru\xe1\xb9\xa3am upaiti divyam 8.10  \n  \nyad ak\xe1\xb9\xa3ara\xe1\xb9\x83 vedavido vadanti  \nvi\xc5\x9banti yad yatayo v\xc4\xabtar\xc4\x81g\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nyad icchanto brahmacarya\xe1\xb9\x83 caranti  \ntat te pada\xe1\xb9\x83 sa\xe1\xb9\x83grahe\xe1\xb9\x87a pravak\xe1\xb9\xa3ye 8.11  \n  \nsarvadv\xc4\x81r\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87i sa\xe1\xb9\x83yamya mano h\xe1\xb9\x9bdi nirudhya ca  \nm\xc5\xabrdhny \xc4\x81dh\xc4\x81y\xc4\x81tmana\xe1\xb8\xa5 pr\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87am \xc4\x81sthito  \nyogadh\xc4\x81ra\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81m 8.12  \n  \nom ity ek\xc4\x81k\xe1\xb9\xa3ara\xe1\xb9\x83 brahma vy\xc4\x81haran m\xc4\x81m anusmaran  \nya\xe1\xb8\xa5 pray\xc4\x81ti tyajan deha\xe1\xb9\x83 sa y\xc4\x81ti param\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 gatim 8.13  \n  \nananyacet\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 satata\xe1\xb9\x83 yo m\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 smarati nitya\xc5\x9ba\xe1\xb8\xa5  \ntasy\xc4\x81ha\xe1\xb9\x83 sulabha\xe1\xb8\xa5 p\xc4\x81rtha nityayuktasya yogina\xe1\xb8\xa5 8.14  \n  \nm\xc4\x81m upetya punarjanma du\xe1\xb8\xa5kh\xc4\x81layam a\xc5\x9b\xc4\x81\xc5\x9bvatam  \nn\xc4\x81pnuvanti mah\xc4\x81tm\xc4\x81na\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa\xe1\xb9\x83siddhi\xe1\xb9\x83 param\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 gat\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n8.15  \n  \n\xc4\x81 brahmabhuvan\xc4\x81l lok\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 punar\xc4\x81vartinorjuna  \nm\xc4\x81m upetya tu kaunteya punarjanma na vidyate 8.16  \n  \nsahasrayugaparyantam ahar yad brahma\xe1\xb9\x87o vidu\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nr\xc4\x81tri\xe1\xb9\x83 yugasahasr\xc4\x81nt\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 te.ahor\xc4\x81travido jan\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 8.17  \n  \navyakt\xc4\x81d vyaktaya\xe1\xb8\xa5 sarv\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 prabhavanty ahar\xc4\x81game  \nr\xc4\x81try\xc4\x81game pral\xc4\xabyante tatraiv\xc4\x81vyaktasa\xe1\xb9\x83j\xc3\xb1ake 8.18  \n  \nbh\xc5\xabtagr\xc4\x81ma\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa ev\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb9\x83 bh\xc5\xabtv\xc4\x81 bh\xc5\xabtv\xc4\x81 pral\xc4\xabyate  \nr\xc4\x81try\xc4\x81gameva\xc5\x9ba\xe1\xb8\xa5 p\xc4\x81rtha prabhavaty ahar\xc4\x81game 8.19  \n  \nparas tasm\xc4\x81t tu bh\xc4\x81vonyovyaktovyakt\xc4\x81t san\xc4\x81tana\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nya\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa sarve\xe1\xb9\xa3u bh\xc5\xabte\xe1\xb9\xa3u na\xc5\x9byatsu na vina\xc5\x9byati 8.20  \n  \navyaktok\xe1\xb9\xa3ara ity uktas tam \xc4\x81hu\xe1\xb8\xa5 param\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 gatim  \nya\xe1\xb9\x83 pr\xc4\x81pya na nivartante tad dh\xc4\x81ma parama\xe1\xb9\x83 mama  \n8.21  \n  \npuru\xe1\xb9\xa3a\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa para\xe1\xb8\xa5 p\xc4\x81rtha bhakty\xc4\x81 labhyas tv ananyay\xc4\x81  \nyasy\xc4\x81nta\xe1\xb8\xa5sth\xc4\x81ni bh\xc5\xabt\xc4\x81ni yena sarvam ida\xe1\xb9\x83 tatam 8.22  \n  \nyatra k\xc4\x81le tv an\xc4\x81v\xe1\xb9\x9bttim \xc4\x81v\xe1\xb9\x9btti\xe1\xb9\x83 caiva yogina\xe1\xb8\xa5  \npray\xc4\x81t\xc4\x81 y\xc4\x81nti ta\xe1\xb9\x83 k\xc4\x81la\xe1\xb9\x83 vak\xe1\xb9\xa3y\xc4\x81mi bharatar\xe1\xb9\xa3abha 8.23  \n  \nagnir jotir aha\xe1\xb8\xa5 \xc5\x9bukla\xe1\xb8\xa5 \xe1\xb9\xa3a\xe1\xb9\x87m\xc4\x81s\xc4\x81 uttar\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb9\x87am  \ntatra pray\xc4\x81t\xc4\x81 gacchanti brahma brahmavido jan\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n8.24  \n  \ndh\xc5\xabmo r\xc4\x81tris tath\xc4\x81 k\xe1\xb9\x9b\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\x87a\xe1\xb8\xa5 \xe1\xb9\xa3a\xe1\xb9\x87m\xc4\x81s\xc4\x81 dak\xe1\xb9\xa3i\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81yanam  \ntatra c\xc4\x81ndramasa\xe1\xb9\x83 jyotir yog\xc4\xab pr\xc4\x81pya nivartate 8.25  \n  \n\xc5\x9buklak\xe1\xb9\x9b\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\x87e gat\xc4\xab hy ete jagata\xe1\xb8\xa5 \xc5\x9b\xc4\x81\xc5\x9bvate mate  \nekay\xc4\x81 y\xc4\x81ty an\xc4\x81v\xe1\xb9\x9bttim anyay\xc4\x81vartate puna\xe1\xb8\xa5 8.26  \n  \nnaite s\xe1\xb9\x9bt\xc4\xab p\xc4\x81rtha j\xc4\x81nan yog\xc4\xab muhyati ka\xc5\x9bcana  \ntasm\xc4\x81t sarve\xe1\xb9\xa3u k\xc4\x81le\xe1\xb9\xa3u yogayukto bhav\xc4\x81rjuna 8.27  \n  \nvede\xe1\xb9\xa3u yaj\xc3\xb1e\xe1\xb9\xa3u tapa\xe1\xb8\xa5su caiva  \nd\xc4\x81ne\xe1\xb9\xa3u yat pu\xe1\xb9\x87yaphala\xe1\xb9\x83 pradi\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadam  \natyeti tat sarvam ida\xe1\xb9\x83 viditv\xc4\x81  \nyog\xc4\xab para\xe1\xb9\x83 sth\xc4\x81nam upaiti c\xc4\x81dyam 8.28  \n  \n\n* * *\n\n[Next: IX. atha navamodhy\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb8\xa5. (r\xc4\x81javidy\xc4\x81r\xc4\x81jaguhyayoga\xe1\xb8\xa5)](bgs09.htm)\n\n'